The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Sports | Buzz over Chappell
                                                   Buzz over Chappell
            A STAFF REPORTER                      
	Calcutta: Greg Chappell could be in the city next month to recruit youngsters for the Rajasthan Cricket Association Academy in Jaipur. The former Team India coach, who is now in charge of the academy, is expected around March 15.         
	The selection will take place at the Town Club ground.                                                                                                                       
